Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.routing.graphhopper.extended

Class ExtendedGHRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.graphhopper.GHRequest
      • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.routing.graphhopper.extended.ExtendedGHRequest
  • public class ExtendedGHRequest
extends com.graphhopper.GHRequest
    Extends GHRequest by providing instances of weighting and algorithms preparation instead of defining string constants. Additionally the number of alternative routes can be set in this request.
